is_online.description: Whether the User is actively connected to this Conversations Service and online. This value is `null` if the Service's `reachability_enabled` is `false`, if the User has never been online for this Conversations Service, even if the Service's `reachability_enabled` is `true`.

role_sid.description: The SID of a service-level [Role](https://www.twilio.com/docs/conversations/api/role-resource) assigned to the user.

sid.description: The unique string that we created to identify the User resource.

url.description: An absolute API resource URL for this user.
